    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>W.A.R.D</strong> is an online co-op fantasy game set in a magical world of floating islands and flying ships. You and your wizard buddies must explore a world ravaged by the <strong>calamity</strong>, perform missions for the <strong>Wizarding Anomaly Resolution Department </strong>and uncover the truth hidden by forces unseen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Congratulations Cadet! As a brand new recruit of the<strong> Wizarding Anomaly Resolution Department</strong> you are joining the ranks of the esteemed Wizards that have served before you in this prestigious organization. Perhaps your luck will be greater than theirs.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You and your fellow wizards must traverse a world of magical mystery. Explore flying islands, abandoned wizard outposts, and other eerie encounters. Battle gravity, magical beasts and the arcane forces themselves while you perform your missions, acquire resources, upgrade your ship, and purchase equipment or enhancements for your characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/eceff0bf7084a8a26ac7340408d27889.webp?t=1767602327\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your world was ravaged by the <strong>calamity</strong> long before your time. Yet, curiously, it still holds many mysterious locations for you to explore. Wizarding castles, haunted by the failed experiments of its previous inhabitants, ravaged abandoned towns where only the ghosts of the past still echoes. Though seemingly deserted, they are filled with hazards you must overcome to reap the rewards and successfully perform your missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/bca0a522c8a4e43d029c4bc64bfc4978.poster.avif?t=1767602327\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/bca0a522c8a4e43d029c4bc64bfc4978.webm?t=1767602327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/bca0a522c8a4e43d029c4bc64bfc4978.mp4?t=1767602327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform missions for the W.A.R.D.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles, gather loot, and avoid dangers together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome Gravity using your acrobatic skills.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the hidden mystery behind your ruined world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/7f1c8943ad7230d5aba53e831b5566ce.webp?t=1767602327\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As novice wizards a world full of magic awaits you.<br>Discover the depth of an intricate spell casting system that allows you to chain elements and modifiers together to perform custom spells on demand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced spell-casting system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine elements and modifiers to perform truly unique and adaptable spells for every situation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find new spell components and upgrade your magic level as you rise within the ranks of wizards.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/cd78d06589ac831aee4f1869efb52e9b.webp?t=1767602327\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ship is your home. Take good care of it, and it will carry you safely on your journey. Store your loot, visit shops, and buy new equipment and upgrades that will aid you along the way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/5730839f791aef179f33a1c8c68c3d7c.poster.avif?t=1767602327\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/5730839f791aef179f33a1c8c68c3d7c.webm?t=1767602327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/5730839f791aef179f33a1c8c68c3d7c.mp4?t=1767602327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Man and pilot your ship between locations.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear up and assign roles when dealing with encounters.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/bd82438b8a74dc08e10b22d472ea89ea.webp?t=1767602327\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teamwork is key to your survival. Solve puzzles together and rely on your friends to save you from the dangers lurking in the locations you visit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/3779792b640c8aebfee6c10259777ef4.poster.avif?t=1767602327\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/3779792b640c8aebfee6c10259777ef4.webm?t=1767602327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/3779792b640c8aebfee6c10259777ef4.mp4?t=1767602327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game proximity voice chat.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collaborative battles, interactions, puzzles, and challenges to overcome together.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/0a7dc2469f226181da64703aba2d51ac.webp?t=1767602327\" width=650 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And lastly, remember that having fun is always the ultimate goal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/e7e05f78a50492e65f0fea8f97403ef7.poster.avif?t=1767602327\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/e7e05f78a50492e65f0fea8f97403ef7.webm?t=1767602327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025030/extras/e7e05f78a50492e65f0fea8f97403ef7.mp4?t=1767602327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
